    "name": "ETH RWA market - set LTVs on existing USDC/USDT borrow vaults",
    "description": "Adds the six new RWA EVaults as collateral on the existing multisig-governed USDC and USDT borrow vaults. Execute only after 03-resolve-new-evaults-on-mainnet-router.json has executed and the six new EVault share tokens quote successfully through the shared EulerRouter. This payload does not configure the new vaults themselves and does not enable mAPOLLO borrowing."
